<h1>Destination info:</h1>

<h2>Name: <%= @destination.name %></h2>
<h2>Country: <%= @destination.country %></h2>

<h2>This destinations featured post is: <%= link_to @destination.featured_post.title, post_path(@destination.featured_post) %></h2>

<h3>The average age of bloggers who have written about this destination is: <%= @destination.average_age %></h3>

<h3>The most recent 5 posts written about this destination are: <%= @destination.five_recent_posts.map{ |post| post.title} %></h3>
